                "type": "scale",
                "options": ["Not at all", "Several days", "More than half the days", "Nearly every day"]
            },
            {
                "id": "gad7_3",
                "text": "Worrying too much about different things?",
                "type": "scale",
                "options": ["Not at all", "Several days", "More than half the days", "Nearly every day"]
            },
            {
                "id": "gad7_4",
