                "type": "scale",
                "options": ["Not at all", "Several days", "More than half the days", "Nearly every day"]
            },
            {
                "id": "gad7_5",
                "text": "Being so restless that it is hard to sit still?",
                "type": "scale",
                "options": ["Not at all", "Several days", "More than half the days", "Nearly every day"]
            },
            {
                "id": "gad7_6",
                "text": "Becoming easily annoyed or irritable?",
                "type": "scale",
                "options": ["Not at all", "Several days", "More than half the days", "Nearly every day"]
